<br>
Anyways, after John read, the slam started. Seven people signed up for it. All the readers were judged. After the 7 readers read, the 4 readers with the highest scores read again (actually 3 because there was a 3-way tie). They were judged once again, &amp; then it was down to the 2 highest scoring readers. The 2 remaining readers read once more. After that prizes were given to readers who ended up in 3rd, 2nd, &amp; 1st places.<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.bbarden.com/em/grin.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
It was all alot of fun!! Alot of cool poems were read. These slams, we found out, happen only once a year. It's too bad they don't happen more often, it was a blast!!<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :bounce --><img src=http://www.bbarden.com/em/bounce.gif ALT=":bounce"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><span class=m><i></i></span><hr size=1><span class=m> </span></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003399><td colspan=2><table cellpadding=8 cellspacing=0 width=100%><tr><td nowrap width=20% valign=top><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub76.ezboard.com/usilvaranger.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SilvaRanger</A> </span><br> <span class=usertitle>Evaporation<br /><img src=http://www.bbarden.com/core_images/userlevels/userlevel-3-1.gif /></span><br> <BR><img src=http://www.urbanvagabond.net/silva/Poems/smallfairy.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top width=80% class=m><span class=title>   Re: I'm going to a poetry slam...</span><br><span class=m><font color=#99CCFF>Posted: 3/21/02 10:25:41 pm</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>    <hr size=1> Glad you had fun Starry, it sounds like a great way to make poems more popular, though I dont think I'd dare to stand up and have my poems errr judged. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.bbarden.com/em/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
